description: Bucky`s Dunsparce was first seen popping out of its tunnel. Togepi and Pikachu spotted it and alerted everyone else. Bucky wasn`t able to capture it immediately as Team Rocket captured it in their net. After Team Rocket was defeated and all the captured Dunsparce were released, the wild Dunsparce appeared again and Bucky was able to capture it.
name: Nokocchi (Kiichi)
